Job Description
A Data Analyst, Edge Office is needed to plan, execute, and manage the work of designing, codifying, and implementing processes and systems that are optimized and digitized to the extent possible.
In this role, you will:
Develop mastery in Edge processes and tools with emphasis on Problem Solving Process, Visual and Daily Management, and Transactional Process Improvement;
Continue to improve upon our in house problem solving (Edge) tools;
Roll out these processes and tools within Success Academy as the enterprise’s standard continuous improvement methodology;
Facilitate Success Academy’s embrace of this standard methodology through application and delivery of both formal and informal trainings;
Drive targeted and radical improvements by applying the Edge methodologies;
Provide informal and formal counsel to Success Academy’s teams on how best to apply Edge methodologies and think differently about the work;
Ensure effective project and change management processes to drive sustainable improvements.
